{
  "chapter": 42,
  "chapter_summary": "小鱼儿离开海家班后流浪到一个城镇，在四海春饭馆当洗碗工，后因炒菜手艺高超被提拔为掌勺大师傅。饭馆迎来三湘武林盟主铁无双宴席，两河联镖总镖头赵全海与三湘镖联的衡山鹰厉峰因镖银之争发生冲突，铁无双以德服人化解争端。然而赵全海和厉峰突然中毒倒地，铁无双也束手无策。小鱼儿旁观时发现铁无双的紫衣白面弟子偷偷溜进厨房与一黑衣人接头，黑衣人的声音与江玉郎极为相似。小鱼儿用移穴大法躲过黑衣人的点穴暗算，从黑衣人提到的暗号和毒药特征判断出是雪魄精之毒。他用焦炭在围裙上写下解毒药方抛给铁无双后飘然离去，决心等到实力足够时再重新亮相江湖。小鱼儿站在江岸思念海家班，却遇到金狮李迪、李明生和紫面狮李挺，三人正在江边等候黑衣人前来接头。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你莫要怪我，这也是没法子的事……我虽然也不愿意走，但我的行踪已露，再也没法子呆在你那里了。",
      "tone": "叹",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_lian_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "圆脸汉子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "对不起，我没有看见你。",
      "tone": "赔笑",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_yuan_lian_han_zi",
      "text": "没关系。",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_lian_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "圆脸汉子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我这里还有些饭，你要是不嫌脏，就进来吃吧。",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_yuan_lian_han_zi",
      "text": "好，谢谢你。",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_lian_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "圆脸汉子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我这里还少个洗碗的人，你要是愿意做，每天少不了有你吃的。",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_yuan_lian_han_zi",
      "text": "我吃得很多。",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_lian_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "圆脸汉子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "开饭馆的，还怕大肚汉么？",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_chang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "张长贵",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "自然是我做的。",
      "tone": "硬着头皮",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "彭老板",
      "listener": "char_zhang_chang_gui",
      "text": "那味道不对，不是你的手艺。",
      "tone": "瞪眼",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "彭老板",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "佩服，佩服，瞧不出你小小年纪，竟能做出那样的菜，连熊老板吃了都拍手叫好，从今天起，你来掌勺吧。",
      "tone": "挑拇指",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_peng_lao_ban",
      "text": "我不会。",
      "tone": "垂头",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "彭老板",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你就帮我个忙吧，从今以后，四海春就得靠你了。",
      "tone": "拍肩",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "彭老板",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "俞老弟，今天你可得分外卖力才是——你猜今天有些什么人来了？",
      "tone": "搓手笑",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_peng_lao_ban",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "淡淡",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "彭老板",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "三湘地方的一条英雄好汉今天居然赏光来到这里，这不但是我的面子，更是你老弟的光彩。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_peng_lao_ban",
      "text": "他又是谁？",
      "tone": "心一动",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_peng_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "彭老板",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "铁无双铁老爷子，江湖人称爱才如命，三湘子弟只要提起这名字，谁人不知，哪个不晓？",
      "tone": "挑拇指",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_peng_lao_ban",
      "text": "哦，是么？",
      "tone": "淡淡",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_quan_hai",
      "speaker_name": "赵全海",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今日兄弟应铁老前辈之召而来，本该老老实实坐在这里喝得大醉而归，但在未醉之前，兄弟心里却有几句话，实在不能不说。",
      "tone": "大声",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": "char_zhao_quan_hai",
      "text": "说，你只管说，不说话怎么喝得下酒。",
      "tone": "捋须笑",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_quan_hai",
      "speaker_name": "赵全海",
      "listener": "char_li_feng",
      "text": "段合肥要运往关外的那批镖银，本是咱们两河联镖先派人到合肥去接下来的，江湖中人人都知道此事。",
      "tone": "瞪眼大声",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_feng",
      "speaker_name": "厉峰",
      "listener": "char_zhao_quan_hai",
      "text": "不错，在下也听说过。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_quan_hai",
      "speaker_name": "赵全海",
      "listener": "char_li_feng",
      "text": "厉总镖头既然知道此事，便不该再派人到合肥去，将这笔生意抢下来，兄弟久闻衡山鹰厉峰乃是仁义英雄，谁知……哼！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_feng",
      "speaker_name": "厉峰",
      "listener": "char_zhao_quan_hai",
      "text": "做买卖讲究货比货，这和江湖道义并没有什么关系，段合肥既然要找三湘镖联，在下也没得法子。",
      "tone": "淡淡",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_quan_hai",
      "speaker_name": "赵全海",
      "listener": "char_li_feng",
      "text": "如此说来，你是说咱们两河联镖比不上你们三湘镖联了？",
      "tone": "怒",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_feng",
      "speaker_name": "厉峰",
      "listener": "char_zhao_quan_hai",
      "text": "在下并未如此说，这全要看别人的意思。",
      "tone": "冷冷",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_quan_hai",
      "speaker_name": "赵全海",
      "listener": "char_li_feng",
      "text": "好……很好！……",
      "tone": "咬牙",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_quan_hai",
      "speaker_name": "赵全海",
      "listener": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "text": "兄弟今日虽然应召而来，但也知道铁老爷子与三湘镖联关系深厚，也不想求铁老爷子为兄弟主持公道。只是……只是三湘镖联既然如此瞧不起两河联镖，咱们少不得要和他们斗一斗，尤其是姓厉的……",
      "tone": "拍桌大喝",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": "char_zhao_quan_hai",
      "text": "赵老弟，我先敬你一杯如何！",
      "tone": "纵声大笑",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": "char_zhao_quan_hai",
      "text": "兄弟你说得不错，老夫世居湘潭，三湘武林中人，可说大多与老夫有些关系，厉峰算起来更可说是老夫的师侄！既然如此，老夫今日若是让老弟你就此负气而去，岂非白混了几十年江湖。",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": "char_li_feng",
      "text": "老夫若要你将这票生意让给两河联镖，你意下如何？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_feng",
      "speaker_name": "厉峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "text": "这……这……",
      "tone": "面色大变",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": "char_li_feng",
      "text": "老夫决不会勉强于你，但这件事老夫已调查清楚，确实是你理亏。你今日若肯接纳老夫之言，老夫便将衡山那片茶林，让作三湘镖联属下的公益……江湖之中，仁义为先，你还是再思，三思！",
      "tone": "正色",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_feng",
      "speaker_name": "厉峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "text": "老爷子的话，弟子怎敢不听，但那茶林乃是老爷子所剩下的少数产业之一，弟子怎敢接受……",
      "tone": "叹",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": "char_li_feng",
      "text": "只要你肯顾念武林道义，莫教我三湘子弟在江湖中被人背后指骂，我老头子那区区产业，又算得什么！",
      "tone": "拊掌大笑",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_quan_hai",
      "speaker_name": "赵全海",
      "listener": "char_li_feng",
      "text": "铁老爷子如此大仁大义，而弟子却……却……弟子实在惭愧，这票生意，还是由三湘镖联承保吧。",
      "tone": "满面愧色",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_feng",
      "speaker_name": "厉峰",
      "listener": "char_zhao_quan_hai",
      "text": "在下不敢，这票生意是两河联镖先接手的，自然还是让两河承保，赵总镖头若再谦谢，反令在下惭愧。",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位既然如此谦让，这趟镖不如就由两河联镖与三湘镖联联保，岂非更是皆大欢喜。",
      "tone": "拊掌大笑",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_quan_hai",
      "speaker_name": "赵全海",
      "listener": "char_li_feng",
      "text": "厉兄，但望此次你我能同心合力，从今以后……",
      "tone": "举杯笑",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_quan_hai",
      "speaker_name": "赵全海",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不好，中毒……总镖头中毒了！",
      "tone": "失声",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这……这是怎么回事？",
      "tone": "面色大变",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_feng",
      "speaker_name": "厉峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你这是在说谁？他吃过的酒菜咱们也吃过，难道……",
      "tone": "拍案怒",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣白面少年",
      "listener": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "text": "莫非是这菜馆里的人？……",
      "tone": "冷冷",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": "char_zi_yi_shao_nian",
      "text": "依我看来，这毒药断非中土所有，否则我行走江湖数十年，怎会连见都未曾见过？若是我猜得不错，这……",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你猜得的确不错，这毒药确非中土所有，乃是天山雪魄精！",
      "tone": "大声",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "围裙上所写的药方，可解雪魄精毒，快去配药，还可有救！",
      "tone": "大声",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好快的身手！",
      "tone": "失声",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雪魄精，居然是雪魄精……难怪我猜不到？",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣白面少年",
      "listener": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "text": "说不定这也是那恶人的诡计！",
      "tone": "冷冷",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你可知道，冻死的人在临死之前，非但不会觉得寒冷，反会觉得如同被烈火焚烧一般，这种感觉若非身历其境，别人永远不会想到的。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣白面少年",
      "listener": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "text": "那么你老人家又怎会知道？",
      "tone": "忍不住",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": "char_zi_yi_shao_nian",
      "text": "只因我也险些被冻死过一次。",
      "tone": "缓缓",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_mian_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白面少年",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "残云。",
      "tone": "轻声",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_bai_mian_shao_nian",
      "text": "风卷残云。",
      "tone": "应声",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_bai_mian_shao_nian",
      "text": "事成了么？",
      "tone": "哑声",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_mian_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白面少年",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "成了。",
      "tone": "简短",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_bai_mian_shao_nian",
      "text": "好。",
      "tone": "简短",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这人是谁？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_mian_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白面少年",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "只不过一个厨子。",
      "tone": "不在意",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "留他不得！",
      "tone": "冷",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "谁叫你呆在这里，你自寻死路，却怨不得我！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_bai_mian_shao_nian",
      "text": "快出去，莫要被人猜疑。",
      "tone": "冷",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_mian_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "白面少年",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_shi_li_di",
      "speaker_name": "李迪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来是个小叫化子。",
      "tone": "皱眉",
      "chapter": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ming_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "李明生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你站在这里干什么？",
